text.tspan: // 150% architectural feature model based on the hierarchical component model of the architecture (see algorithm for more details)

text.tspan: // correspondence between architectural elements and plugins: propositional constraints (generated by the algorithm)

g.text: fmFull = aggregate { fm150 fmPlugin } withMapping mappings

text.tspan: // by default, the root name is the identifier of the variable
